00:00:20.010 --> 00:00:23.910
Kim, tell us about being an ER nurse ñ specifically
an ER nurse.

00:00:23.910 --> 00:00:26.429
Whatís a typical day for an ER nurse?

00:00:26.429 --> 00:00:32.110
Kim McAllister: A typical day in the ER is
